premise_source_doc_sentence: Minaj 's first and second studio albums , Pink Friday  (  2010  )  and Pink Friday : Roman Reloaded  (  2012  )  , both peaked at number one on the U.S. Billboard 200 and produced the successful singles `` Super Bass '' and `` Starships '' , respectively .

The album was supported by the singles ; `` We Alright '' featuring Lil Wayne , Birdman and Euro , `` Senile '' featuring Tyga , Nicki Minaj and Lil Wayne , `` Trophies '' featuring Drake and `` Lookin Ass '' featuring Nicki Minaj .
